<p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">相机快门轻响</span></p><p><strong>“咔嚓”“咔嚓”~</strong></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">四年时光突然有了具象的形状</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">那些与校园相伴的晨昏</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">成为记忆中永不褪色的青春注脚</span></p><p><strong>快门里的大学时光</strong></p><p><br></p><p>校园里的绿意与教学楼的古朴相映成趣</p><p>藏着我们四年的晨昏</p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756992755542.png" alt="1756992755542.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756992755542.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756992795684.png" alt="1756992795684.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756992795684.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756992809960.png" alt="1756992809960.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756992809960.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993513874.png" alt="1756993513874.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993513874.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993524440.png" alt="1756993524440.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993524440.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993627220.png" alt="1756993627220.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993627220.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993639299.png" alt="1756993639299.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993639299.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>原来那些被我们记住的日常</p><p>早已刻进时光的胶卷</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993652341.png" alt="1756993652341.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993652341.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993661516.png" alt="1756993661516.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993661516.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993669458.png" alt="1756993669458.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993669458.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>才惊觉：</p><p>原来我们早已把自己的青春</p><p>种在了这片土地的每一个角落</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993676592.png" alt="1756993676592.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993676592.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993683766.png" alt="1756993683766.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993683766.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993690401.png" alt="1756993690401.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993690401.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>与校园合影的独家记忆</strong></p><p><br></p><p>热浪席卷校园</p><p>蝉鸣织就毕业的序章</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993714761.png" alt="1756993714761.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993714761.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993720518.png" alt="1756993720518.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993720518.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993727932.png" alt="1756993727932.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993727932.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993733574.png" alt="1756993733574.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993733574.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993740434.png" alt="1756993740434.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993740434.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993749865.png" alt="1756993749865.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993749865.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>在标志性的打卡点</p><p>把蓬勃的生命力框进镜头</p><p>有人把学士帽抛向天空</p><p>帽檐划过的弧线里</p><p>是 <strong>“从此山高水长” </strong>的憧憬</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993755587.png" alt="1756993755587.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993755587.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993762414.png" alt="1756993762414.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993762414.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>有人在湖畔并肩而坐</p><p>倒影里是 “一起走过无数日夜” 的默契</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993769866.png" alt="1756993769866.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993769866.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993779329.png" alt="1756993779329.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993779329.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>此刻都在镜头前笑得坦荡</p><p>江西软件大学的风</p><p>终究是吹熟了我们的年少轻狂</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993882209.png" alt="1756993882209.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993882209.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993889192.png" alt="1756993889192.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993889192.png" style=""/></p><p><strong>校园里的时光胶囊</strong></p><p>想倒带回放每个平凡晨昏</p><p>橘黄灯光下书页的字字耕耘</p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993903161.png" alt="1756993903161.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993903161.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993912625.png" alt="1756993912625.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993912625.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993919050.png" alt="1756993919050.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993919050.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>运动场上的夕阳流光</p><p>志愿活动时的汗水笑颜</p><p>泡在研究室里的废寝忘食</p><p>还有和好友放肆欢笑的点点滴滴……</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993944458.png" alt="1756993944458.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993944458.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993950517.png" alt="1756993950517.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993950517.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993956224.png" alt="1756993956224.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993956224.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>原来“先锋回忆”</p><p>从不是某个高光时刻</p><p>而是无数个平凡日子里</p><p>与江西软件大学共同生长的痕迹</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993962797.png" alt="1756993962797.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993962797.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993970505.png" alt="1756993970505.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993970505.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993977235.png" alt="1756993977235.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993977235.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993983437.png" alt="1756993983437.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993983437.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993989494.png" alt="1756993989494.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993989494.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><strong>终章：向时光告白</strong></p><p><br></p><p>“3、2、1——”</p><p>学士帽抛出的瞬间</p><p>真的要结束了</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993996919.png" alt="1756993996919.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756993996919.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756994006151.png" alt="1756994006151.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756994006151.png" style=""/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>就像告别一场漫长的电影</p><p>告别的不只是六月的蝉鸣</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>是那个在图书馆奋笔疾书的自己</p><p>那个在技能大赛上为团队拼搏的自己</p><p>那个在校园里憧憬未来的自己</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756994019770.png" alt="1756994019770.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756994019770.png" style=""/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">离开江西软件职业技术大学的夏天</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">愿你的故事如校园的风景般独特</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">如盛夏阳光般炽热</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">当多年后翻开这组毕业照</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">仍能听见那年六月的风</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">在耳边轻轻说：</span></p><p><strong>“咔嚓 —— 这一夏，</strong></p><p><strong>我们曾如此热烈地绽放过。”</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>